2. no way in bloody hell should mage pets get any more powerful.  Your fooling yourself if you think your pet in any way shape or form from level 1-60 is &quot;underpowered&quot;. Your pet is easily 70% of a melee, and you are at least 50% of a wizard.  Only in raids agianst FR/MR mobs are mages not as useful. (and even then you just having stacking problems, not that your class is unneeded)<br>
